dc_title_s: Ramsey, New Jersey--New York. 7.5 minute series (topographic)
dc_description_s: U.S.G.S. 7.5 minute series (topographic) North Decimal Degree 41.125000. South Decimal Degree 41.000000. East Decimal Degree -74.125000. West Decimal Degree -74.250000. Alternate title: Ramsey, NJ--NY. Polyconic projection. Universal transverse Mercator grids are shown. Relief shown by 10 feet contour interval and spot heights. Datum is mean sea level. "Mapped edited and published by the United States Geological Survey. Control by USGS, USC&GS, and New Jersey Geodetic Survey. Topography by planetable surveys 1935-1936, and 1943. Revised 1955." Map is temporarily filed in the Reserve Course Materials Collection.
